{
  "_name": "07 — AI-Generated Image Enhance (KSampler → RTX VSR)",
  "_description": [
    "Full diffusion + RTX VSR pipeline:",
    "  1. Generate a 512x512 or 768x768 image with KSampler (standard SDXL/SD1.5 workflow)",
    "  2. Decode the latent to an IMAGE tensor",
    "  3. Pass directly to RTX VSR 4x upscale",
    "  4. Save the final 2K or 4K result",
